==English==

===Etymology===
{{F.}} ''résigner'', {{L.}} ''resignare'' to unseal, annul, assign, resign; prefix [[re-]] + [[signare]] to seal, stamp.

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aɪn|-aɪn]]

===Verb===
'''to resign'''  ([[resigns]], [[resigned]], [[resigning]])
